hadiths[16]{hadithnumber,text}:
3702,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke merey walid ney mujhey eik ghulam bator Atiya diya, phir wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah bananey key liye aap ki khidmat mein hazir huye. aap ney farmaya : kya tum ney apney tamam bachchon ko Atiya diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir isey bhi wapis ley lo. ye siyaaq Muhammad bin Mansoor ka hai (Quteba bin Saeed maaeney ke sath bayan kartey hain)."
3703,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (Raziallahu anhu) hai ke unkey walid unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey aur kaha : mainey apney us betey ko apna eik ghulam bator Atiya diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum ney apney tamam beton ko Atiya diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir usey bhi wapis karo.
3704,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke unkey walid Hazrat Bashir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) apney betey Noman ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey apney us betey ko apna eik ghulam bator Atiya diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tu ney apney sab beton ko Atiya diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir usey bhi wapis karo.
3705,Hazrat Bashir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Noman bin Bashir ko ley kar Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : mainey apney is betey ko eik ghulam Atiya kiya hai. agar aap isey munasib samajhtey hain to main is atiye ko nafiz (laagu) kar deta hun. aap ney farmaya : kya tu ney apney sab beton ko Atiya kiya hai? mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir isey bhi wapis karo.
3706,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke merey walid ney mujhey eik (ghulam ka) Atiya diya. meri walida un sey kehney lagin : merey betey key atiye par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah bana lein. merey walid Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur puri baat aap sey zikr ki. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is par gawah banna pasand nahin farmaya.
3707,"Hazrat Bashir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apney eik betey ko eik ghulam tohfey mein diya. phir wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko is tohfey par gawah banaeyn. aap ney farmaya : kya tum ney puri aulad ko aisey tohfey diye hain? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya, phir isey bhi wapis kar."
3708,Hazrat Urwa (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Nabi ! mainey Noman ko eik tohfa diya hai. aap ney farmaya : uskey bhaiyon ko bhi diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir isey bhi wapis kar.
3709,"Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke mujhey merey walid mohtaram utha kar Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmate-aaliya mein ley gaey aur arz kya : aap gawah ho jaiye ke mainey Noman ko apney maal sey itna itna tohfa diya hai. aap ney farmaya : kya tum ney apney har betey ko is tarah ka tohfa diya jaisey Noman ko diya hai?"
3710,Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke unkey walid unhen Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey. unka maqsad aap ko us ka Atiya par gawah banana tha jo unhoney usey diya tha. aap ney farmaya : kya tu ney apney sab bachon ko us jaisa tohfa diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : main aisi kisi chiz par gawah nahin bin sakta. kya tujhey ye baat pasand nahin ke wo sab tujh sey Hasan sulook mein barabar hun? unhoney kaha : zarur . aap ney farmaya : to phir sirf eik ko tohfa na dey.
3711,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke un ki walida mohtarma binte Rawaaha ney unkey walid mohtaram sey mutalba kiya ke merey betey ko apney maal mein sey koi Atiya den. wo eik saal tak taal matol kartey rahey. aakhir unkey ji mein aaya to unhoney usey (Noman ko) Atiya dey diya. to uski walida kehney lagi : main us waqt tak razi nahin jab tak tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah nahin banatey. wo aap key paas ja kar kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! iski maa binte Rawaaha (eik saal sey) mujh sey is atiye ki khatir jhagadti rahi hai jo mainey is (Noman) ko diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Bashir ! kya iskey ilawa bhi terey bachchey hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum ney un mein sey har eik ko us jaisa tohfa diya hai jo tu ney apney is betey ko diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir mujhey (is par) gawah na banaao kyonkey main zulm par gawah nahin ban sakta.
3712,"Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke meri walida ney merey liye merey walid sey kisi atiye ka mutalba kiya. unhoney mujhey Atiya dey diya. to wo kehney lagin : main to tab razi hongi jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah banaya jaey. merey walid ney mera haath pakda, main abhi bachcha tha, aur mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! iski walida binte Rawaaha ney iskey liye mujh sey kisi atiye ka mutalba kiya hai aur uski khahish hai ke main aap ko us atiye ka gawah banaaun. aap ney farmaya : aey Bashir ! kya iskey ilawa terey aur betey bhi hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : tu ney unhen bhi aisa Atiya diya hai jaisa isey diya hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir mujhey gawah na banaao kyonkey main zulm par gawah nahin ban sakta."
3713,"Hazrat Aamir Sh'abi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey bataya gaya ke Hazrat Bashir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri biwi Umra binte Rawaaha ney mujhey majbur kiya hai ke main uskey betey Noman ko koi Atiya dun aur phir aap ko us (atiye) par gawah bhi banaun. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya iskey ilawa bhi terey betey hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : tu ney in ko bhi is jaisa tohfa diya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. to aap ney farmaya : mujhey zulm par gawah na banaao."
3714,Hazrat Abdullah bin Utba bin Masood (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : mainey apney betey ko Atiya diya hai. aap gawah ho jaiye. aap ney farmaya : kya iskey ilawa bhi teri aulad hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : kya tum ney iski tarah unhen bhi atiyaat diye hain? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : to kya main zulm par gawah banun?
3715,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they : merey walid mohtaram mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey. wo aap ko us atiye par gawah banana chahtey they jo unhoney mujhey diya tha. aap ney farmaya : kya iskey ilawa teri aur aulad bhi hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney puri hatheli khol kar haath key sath ishara kartey huye farmaya : tu ney in mein barabari kyon na ki?
3716,Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) khutbey mein farma rahey they : mujhey merey walid mohtaram Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaey. wo aap ko us atiye par gawah banana chahtey they jo unhoney mujhey diya tha. aap ney farmaya : kya iskey ilawa bhi terey betey hain? wo kehney lagey : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : phir in mein barabari karo.
3717,Hazrat Mufazzal bin Mohlab sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ko khutbey key doran mein farmatey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney beton key darmiyan insaf karo. apney beton key darmiyan adl karo.
